#include <iostream>
#include <algorithm>
#include <string>
using namespace std;

int main() 
{
	int t,test,n,i;
	cin>>t;
	int hash[20000]={0};
	for(test=0;test<t;test++)
	{
		cin>>n;
		int nos[n];
		
		for(i=0;i<n;i++)cin>>nos[i];
		
		for(i=0;i<20000;i++)hash[i]=0;
		
		
		for(i=n-1;i>=0;i--)
		{
			hash[nos[i]+10000]++;
			if(hash[nos[i]+10000]>1)nos[i]=-10001;
		}
		
		for(i=0;i<n;i++)
		{
			
			if(nos[i]!=-10001)cout<<nos[i]<<"\n";
			
		}
	}
	
}
